reviewText: This dvd did not work and I tried numerous DVD players.

Even if you do not plan on using this technique with another, I highly recommend you read this book. The insights that I learned about the traumatized soul are priceless. As a massage therapist and an EFT practitioner; I will be better equipped to honor the space that my clients come from. And really, just in having conversation with anyone anywhere anytime I now have much more sensitivity.

This will not play in any of my equipment. I have no idea how to return it and I am out a lot of money for this investment. And I just watched a movie last night so I am confident that my equipment is in working order.
Could someone help me?
